<|startoftext|>Dish: green chile turkey chicken
Directions: preheat oven to 350 degrees f
rinse and drain the green chiles
cut off the tops and bottom , cutting each to fit a breast
wash and dry the chicken inside and out
then dip into the flour mix
place on a large baking sheet and bake for 20 - 30 minutes
add the onions and the tomatoes and continue to bake for another 30 - 40 minutes
remove the cover and brush the chicken with the last mixture of chilies and cheese
return to oven to bake for another 15 - 20 minutes or until chicken is well cooked and juices run clear'<|endoftext|>
